HEADWORD: Fungivorous
<hw>Fun*giv"o*rous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>fungus</ets> + <ets>vorare</ets> to eat greedily: cf. F.
<ets>fongivore</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Eating fungi; --
